700
00:35:38,380 --> 00:35:40,080
Dobre!

701
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:50,150
Generál Wu?

702
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:06,159
Oheň!

703
00:36:06,159 --> 00:36:07,491
Prestaňte ho naháňať, choď uhasiť oheň!&

